---
// Services.astro
---

<section id="services" class="relative w-full mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-32 py-16 md:py-32">
    <!-- Background Elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-20 w-72 md:w-96 h-72 md:h-96 bg-accentColor/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-40 left-0 w-52 md:w-72 h-52 md:h-72 bg-accentColor/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-24 md:w-32 h-24 md:h-32 bg-accentColor/20 rounded-lg rotate-12"></div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12 md:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 md:mb-6">
        Digital Marketing Services That Don't Disappoint
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        You deserve the best. And that's what we'll deliver. Our multi-channel marketing services 
        integrate with your existing marketing to make a match made in Ninja Heaven.
      </p>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Services Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-12 md:mb-20">
      <!-- Strategy -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-accentColor/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-accentColor" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white">Strategy</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Dominate against your competitors with a multi-channel marketing strategy devised by our Ninjas. 
          We track your competitors and analyse your market to uncover your juiciest marketing opportunities.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- SEO -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-accentColor/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-accentColor" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white">SEO</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Hit those top spots and sweep away the competition with our renowned SEO service. 
          We'll knock your socks off with future-proof SEO that generates high volumes of qualified traffic.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Website Creation -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-accentColor/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-accentColor" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white">Website Creation</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          High-converting websites that deliver results. Our websites are designed to perform. 
          With a lot of logic and a little bit of magic, they turn visitors into customers.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- PPC Advertising -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-accentColor/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-accentColor" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white">PPC Advertising</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Award-winning PPC services that maximise results. Our test-and-iterate approach to Google Ads, 
          Facebook and paid social ads eeks out the most leads and sales for your budget.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Content Creation -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300 group md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl bg-accentColor/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-accentColor" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white">Content Creation</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Our master writers create content that captivates and converts. We craft everything from website 
          copy and blogs to eBooks and we're comfortable working with technical topics.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="flex justify-center">
        <a href="/#contact">
      <button class="group bg-accentColor text-black px-6 md:px-10 py-3 md:py-4 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl text-base md:text-lg font-medium 
                     transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accentColor/20 duration-300 relative">
        Let's Collaborate â€“ Schedule A Call
        <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/20 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></span>
      </button>
      </a>
    </div>
</section>